<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="義解" xml:id="gsz0748c25shiJuMin"><lb
ed="T" n="0748c25"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0748c25"/><head><date from-iso="+0947-03-15" key="j20670182068464" to-iso="+0951-02-28">漢</date><placeName key="PL000000003781"><placeName>太原</placeName><placeName>崇福寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A009937">巨岷</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0748c26"/><persName key="A009937">釋巨岷</persName>，姓<name>任</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000006221">西河</placeName>人也。父遊于藝<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1216"/>而賁<lb
ed="T" n="0748c27"/>丘園<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1217"/>。母<persName key="A022493">王<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>戒受八關<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1218"/>，心歸三寶，從妊<persName key="A009937">岷</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0748c28"/>也，更好善緣，復求福利，而生令<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1219"/>子。及生，年<lb
ed="T" n="0748c29"/>甫<ref type="date" target="#j20436152043969">七歲</ref>，志氣敦篤，暫見佛像，注仰欣然。父母<pb ed="T" n="0749a" xml:id="T50.2061.0749a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0749a01"/>知有宿因，或携入寺，意欲忘歸。至本郡<placeName key="PL000000006205">淨<lb
ed="T" n="0749a02"/>心院</placeName>，見<persName key="A009938">宣遠<roleName>論師</roleName></persName>，志戀其房，泣求攝受。二<lb
ed="T" n="0749a03"/>親知不能阻其願，咸皆可之。<ref type="date" target="#j20447082045061">年十歲</ref>，誦終<lb
ed="T" n="0749a04"/>《法華》、《維摩》二經，日持十卷，更無間隔，如執<lb
ed="T" n="0749a05"/>瑠璃之器。其舒徐<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1220"/><anchor xml:id="beg0749001"/>恣<anchor xml:id="end0749001"/>制<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1221"/>，若老成<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g672"/>焉。迨圓滿<lb
ed="T" n="0749a06"/>足<ptr type="glossary" target="#g33"/>，便習尸羅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g904"/>，克<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g560"/>通開制<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1222"/>之科，恒照欣戚之<lb
ed="T" n="0749a07"/>鑑。自爾大乘理趣，經論精窮，得其師門，則<placeName key="PL000000005942"><placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0749sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>並</sic><corr>并</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0749sgsz1"/><lb
ed="T" n="0749a08"/>部</placeName><placeName>永和</placeName></placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g2176"/>三學<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g182"/>也。俾夜作晝，窓案是臨，不暇<lb
ed="T" n="0749a09"/>諸他。除研習義章，修六事<ptr type="glossary" target="#g935"/>二因<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1223"/>也，於《大般<lb
ed="T" n="0749a10"/>涅槃經》兼《因明論》<ptr target="#n1184"/>，<anchor xml:id="beg0749sgsz2"/>末<anchor xml:id="end0749sgsz2"/>年逾切。又傳輸《金論》<ptr target="#n1224"/>，盡<lb
ed="T" n="0749a11"/>屏餘緣，各講十遍，仍求輔亮<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1225"/>，博覽群書，得<lb
ed="T" n="0749a12"/>義最精，又揚具美。尋稟綸言<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1226"/>，住城內<placeName key="PL000000003789">天王<lb
ed="T" n="0749a13"/>院</placeName>，與弟子俱供億<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1227"/>不虧，傳持無替<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g522"/>。<date from-iso="+0948-03-15" key="j20673842067711" to-iso="+0949-02-05"><name>乾祐</name>元<lb
ed="T" n="0749a14"/>年</date>，<persName key="A006582">漢祖</persName>以龍潛<placeName key="PL000000003731">晉</placeName>土之日，便仰<persName key="A009937">岷</persName>名，特降<lb
ed="T" n="0749a15"/>庭臣賜紫衣，號<persName key="A009937">圓智大師</persName>。續有詔宣住<placeName key="PL000000003782"><placeName>崇<lb
ed="T" n="0749a16"/>福寺</placeName><placeName>講堂院</placeName></placeName>，仍充管內僧正。經年而變法<lb
ed="T" n="0749a17"/>於<placeName key="PL000000003731">晉</placeName>，檢策僧徒，如風偃草。至<date key="j20680112068011" when-iso="+0949-12-02"><name>乾祐</name>二年十<lb
ed="T" n="0749a18"/>一月五日</date>，無疾而終。于時四眾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g98"/>含悲，一城戀<lb
ed="T" n="0749a19"/>德。俗齡<anchor xml:id="beg0749002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>九</sic><corr>七</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0749002"/>十三<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n249"/>，法臘五十四。乃遵西域<anchor xml:id="beg0749sgsz3"/>茶<lb
ed="T" n="0749a20"/>毘<anchor xml:id="end0749sgsz3"/>禮，多投香水，或執旛花，黑白之眾盈郊，<lb
ed="T" n="0749a21"/>黯䨴<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1228"/>之雲蔽日，未容火滅，皆捧寶瓶，待<lb
ed="T" n="0749a22"/>盛梁粟之形，同見熏修之體。時得舍利者，<lb
ed="T" n="0749a23"/>隨自因緣，或多或<anchor xml:id="beg0749sgsz4"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>小</sic><corr>少</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0749sgsz4"/>。別得遺骨，具表奏聞。<lb
ed="T" n="0749a24"/><ref type="person" target="#A006583"><name>漢</name>主</ref>勅葬於<placeName key="PL000000003788"><placeName>西山</placeName><placeName>天龍寺</placeName></placeName>，凡事官供，起石<lb
ed="T" n="0749a25"/>塔。勅謚號曰<persName key="A009937">達識</persName>焉。</p>
